description:
We require a trainee IT Sales Person to join our regional office in Ashford, Kent. The successful candidate will enjoy a rewards package including basic salary, achievable commission structure, company vehicle and personal development opportunities within the MyCorp Group of Companies. 

In return we require you to be :-
•	Professional
•	Presentable
•	Self-motivated
•	Hold a full UK driving licence
•	Communicative
•	Able to work as part of a team

You may have a  knowledge of IT but this is not essential as training will be provided;
You should be able to demonstrate a successful track record of above target sales performance;

You will be required to identify and develop new business opportunities;
You will be required to optimise IT sales opportunities within existing accounts;
You will be expected to develop an overall perspective of the clients’ total office equipment requirements;
You will be expected to consistently perform above target:

Still interested? Then in the first instance send in your CV
